high_descs: Turn left and move to the gray coffee maker to the right of the lettuce, then move to the silver dishwasher to the right of the black toaster.
Pick up the yellow handled knife to the left of the square plate from the counter.
Turn around and move to the sink to the right of the loaf of bread.
Place the knife in the sink to the left of the lettuce, turn on the faucet to rinse the knife, then pick up the knife from the sink.
Turn around and face the dishwasher underneath the green glass.
Place the knife on the plate to the rear of the potato on the counter.
anns.task_desc: Place a clean knife on a plate on the counter.

high_descs: Turn around and move through the room. Turn left and then face the counter on the right, where the dishwasher is.
Pick up the knife from the counter.
Hold the knife and turn around to the sink.
Place the knife in the sink and turn the water on. Turn the water off and pick up the knife.
Carry the knife and turn around to the counter.
Place the knife on the plate, that is on the counter.
anns.task_desc: Rinse a knife and put it on a plate.

high_descs: turn left walk straight then turn left and walk towards the coffee machine and turn left and walk straight towards the dishwasher and turn right
pick up the knife on the counter top
turn right walk straight then turn right towards the sink
put the knife inside the sink and fill it with water then drain the water and remove the knife
turn right then walk straight then turn right again towards the counter
put the knife down on the counter top
anns.task_desc: clean a knife and put it back onto the counter
